&lt;li data-start=&quot;1058&quot; data-end=&quot;1112&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Turn complex concepts into clear, compelling visuals&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1115&quot; data-end=&quot;1182&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Contribute to Glean’s brand system and scalable design frameworks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
