&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Working knowledge of U.S. immigration laws and U.S. benefits regulations&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Experience using HRIS platforms, benefits systems, and ticketing tools&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced environment, independently manage multiple workstreams, and confidently respond to a high volume of immigration-related questions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This role is hybrid (4 days a week in our SF Bay Area offices)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation &amp;amp; Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The standard base salary range for this position is $115,000 - $125,000 annually. Compensation offered will be determined by factors such as location, level, job-related knowledge, skills, and experience. Certain roles may be eligible for variable compensation, equity, and benefits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
