&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This role is hybrid (4 days a week in our SF Bay Area offices)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
