&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Leadership &amp;amp; impact: Track record of shipping successful AI products with measurable impact on user productivity and satisfaction, while guiding and mentoring other designers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
