&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;You have a strong technical background and excel at analytical thinking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
