&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Recognized by Fast Company as one of the World’s Most Innovative Companies (Top 10, 2025), by CNBC’s Disruptor 50, Bloomberg’s AI Startups to Watch (2026), Forbes AI 50, and Gartner’s Tech Innovators in Agentic AI, Glean continues to accelerate its global impact. With customers across 50+ industries and 1,000+ employees in more than 25 countries, we’re helping the world’s largest organizations make every employee AI-fluent, and turning the superintelligent enterprise from concept into reality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If you’re excited to shape how the world works, you’ll help build systems used daily across Microsoft Teams, Zoom, ServiceNow, Zendesk, GitHub, and many more - deeply embedded where people get things done. You’ll ship agentic capabilities on an open, extensible stack, with the craft and care required for enterprise trust, as we bring Work AI to every employee, in every company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Glean is seeking a detail-oriented and experienced Senior Payroll Analyst with a strong background in US payroll operations. The Senior US Payroll Analyst plays a critical role in delivering accurate, compliant, and timely payroll across the US &amp;amp; CA workforce. This position ensures seamless execution of end‑to‑end payroll activities while maintaining adherence to federal, state, and local regulations. The Senior Payroll Analyst also drives process improvement, supports audits, and collaborates with HR, Finance, Accounting, Legal and external partners to resolve complex payroll issues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;You will:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Lead full‑cycle bi‑monthly payroll processing for multi‑state US employees and CA employees, ensuring accuracy for all pay types including regular, overtime, bonuses, commissions, retro payouts, and one‑time transactions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Conduct rigorous pre‑ and post‑payroll audits to verify pay, taxes, deductions, and compliance prior to disbursement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Reconcile payroll results with HRIS data and general ledger, ensuring alignment with accounting and finance requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Maintain deep knowledge of US payroll compliance requirements including federal, state, and local tax laws, wage and hour regulations, and reporting obligations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Prepare and support payroll tax filings, compliance reports, and audits, and assist with remediation of tax notices and discrepancies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ensure accurate handling of garnishments, benefit deductions, and statutory withholdings in payroll processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Senior Payroll Analyst liaison with third‑party payroll vendors, tax advisors, and compliance partners, ensuring SLAs are met and issues are resolved efficiently.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain strong payroll process documentation countrywise, including standard operating procedures (SOPs) and internal controls&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Partner with HR, Finance, Accounting, Legal, Benefits and People Operations teams to ensure seamless payroll operations and alignment with business needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Provide expert payroll support to employees and internal teams, responding to inquiries and resolving issues with professionalism and accuracy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Prepare and present analytical payroll reports and insights to Leadership.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Experience with equity compensation, stock plans, or global payroll processes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Prior experience in SOX / internal controls environments or payroll transformation projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About you:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Finance, Accounting, Business Administration, or a related field.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Minimum 8+ years of progressive payroll experience, with a strong emphasis on multi‑state US payroll processing and compliance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Hands‑on experience with enterprise payroll systems (e.g., Workday, ADP, Rippling)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Advanced proficiency in payroll systems, Excel/Google Sheets (pivot tables, VLOOKUP, formulas)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to manage multiple priorities, tight deadlines, and high‑volume payroll cycles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Payroll certification such as CPP (Certified Payroll Professional) or FPC (Fundamental Payroll Certification) is an added advantage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Strong understanding of US payroll regulations (FLSA, 401k, Garnishment, payroll related benefits deductions, IRS guidelines, multi-state tax compliance).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent analytical, problem-solving, and communication skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Attention to detail and ability to handle confidential information with integrity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This role is hybrid (3 days a week in our Bangalore office)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This role has a shift from 4 PM – 1 AM IST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation &amp;amp; Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Compensation offered will be determined by factors such as location, level, job-related knowledge, skills, and experience. Certain roles may be eligible for variable compensation, equity, and benefits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We are a diverse bunch of people and we want to continue to attract and retain a diverse range of people into our organization. We&#39;re committed to an inclusive and diverse company. We do not discriminate based on gender, ethnicity, sexual orientation, religion, civil or family status, age, disability, or race.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;#LI-HYBRID&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-First Mindset at Glean:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At Glean, AI fluency is core to how we work and we&#39;re committed to ensuring every new hire feels confident integrating AI into their everyday work. &lt;strong&gt;As part of the interview process, you&#39;ll complete a brief AI-focused exercise or discussion so we can understand how you think about, design, and use AI to drive impact in your role. &lt;/strong&gt;Feel free to reference any tools, platforms, or workflows you use today — prior Glean experience isn&#39;t required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Glean:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Glean is the Work AI platform that helps everyone work smarter with AI. What began as the industry’s most advanced enterprise search has evolved into a full-scale Work AI ecosystem, powering intelligent Search, an AI Assistant, and scalable AI agents on one secure, open platform. With over 100 enterprise SaaS connectors, flexible LLM choice, and robust APIs, Glean gives organizations the infrastructure to govern, scale, and customize AI across their entire business - without vendor lock-in or costly implementation cycles.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;At its core, Glean is redefining how enterprises find, use, and act on knowledge. Its Enterprise Graph and Personal Knowledge Graph map the relationships between people, content, and activity, delivering deeply personalized, context-aware responses for every employee. This foundation powers Glean’s agentic capabilities - AI agents that automate real work across teams by accessing the industry’s broadest range of data: enterprise and world, structured and unstructured, historical and real-time. The result: measurable business impact through faster onboarding, hours of productivity gained each week, and smarter, safer decisions at every level.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Recognized by Fast Company as one of the World’s Most Innovative Companies (Top 10, 2025), by CNBC’s Disruptor 50, Bloomberg’s AI Startups to Watch (2026), Forbes AI 50, and Gartner’s Tech Innovators in Agentic AI, Glean continues to accelerate its global impact. With customers across 50+ industries and 1,000+ employees in more than 25 countries, we’re helping the world’s largest organizations make every employee AI-fluent, and turning the superintelligent enterprise from concept into reality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If you’re excited to shape how the world works, you’ll help build systems used daily across Microsoft Teams, Zoom, ServiceNow, Zendesk, GitHub, and many more - deeply embedded where people get things done. You’ll ship agentic capabilities on an open, extensible stack, with the craft and care required for enterprise trust, as we bring Work AI to every employee, in every company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Glean is seeking a Senior Salesforce Developer / Lead Salesforce Engineer with 7–8 years of experience to design, build, and operate scalable Salesforce solutions that power our Sales, Marketing, and Revenue Operations teams. This role is critical to ensuring our Salesforce platform—especially Sales Cloud, Revenue Cloud Advanced (RCA), Salesforce CPQ, and Quote‑to‑Cash (QTC)—is reliable, scalable, and aligned with Glean’s growth. The ideal candidate combines deep hands‑on Salesforce development expertise (Apex, Lightning Web Components, Flows, APIs, CPQ, and Revenue Cloud) with strong ownership, business understanding, and the ability to collaborate across teams to deliver high‑quality, production‑ready solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Design, develop, and deploy custom Salesforce solutions across Sales Cloud, Salesforce CPQ, and core platform services&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Design, develop, and support Revenue Cloud Advanced (RCA) solutions, including advanced pricing, product modeling, and revenue orchestration&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Deliver complex Salesforce initiatives from technical design through production deployment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain custom functionality using Apex, Lightning Web Components (LWC), Flows, and REST/SOAP APIs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Own and enhance Salesforce CPQ and Quote‑to‑Cash (QTC) processes, including pricing, approvals, renewals, and amendments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Configure and extend RCA components such as Product Catalog, Pricing, Promotions, and Discounting frameworks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Build and customize RCA‑driven Quote, Order, and Revenue flows aligned with complex enterprise sales motions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Implement and optimize advanced pricing rules, eligibility logic, and pricing waterfalls using RCA capabilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Support RCA data models and APIs, ensuring seamless integration with Salesforce core objects and downstream billing and revenue systems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Apply strong analytical and problem‑solving skills to debug code, analyze system behavior, and resolve complex technical challenges&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Build and support integrations between Salesforce and downstream systems using APIs, platform events, middleware, and asynchronous patterns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Oversee and support integrations with tools such as ZoomInfo, Marketo, Gong, LeanData, DocuSign, and Apollo.io&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve production issues impacting automation, integrations, data quality, performance, and platform limits&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Write, optimize, and troubleshoot complex SOQL queries to retrieve and manipulate Salesforce data&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Design and implement secure REST/SOAP APIs, callouts, and integrations with external systems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with business, QA, architecture, and operations teams to translate requirements into scalable technical solutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Ensure Salesforce configurations align with security, access control, and data governance standards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Participate in code reviews, CI/CD pipeline activities, release management, and deployments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Establish and monitor KPIs related to platform health, delivery quality, and business outcomes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Drive user adoption through training, documentation, and change management initiatives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Reduce technical debt by refactoring legacy automation and improving system consistency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Stay current with Salesforce technologies, releases, and best practices to implement innovative solutions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Foster a high‑performance, collaborative engineering environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
