&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Design, build, and improve AI/ML systems and data pipelines infrastructure, including platforms that power large language model serving, routing, and orchestration at scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
