&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Write robust code that’s efficient, easy to read, maintain and test&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
