&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Build and iterate joint GTM plans with AWS and GCP, including target accounts, segments, plays, and marketplace priorities for the region.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
