&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Help evolve Cloud Alliances SOPs, playbooks, and dashboards for how we “run with the clouds” globally and in the Americas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
