&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Build the go‑to‑market plan for your territory: target account list, use‑case focus, partner strategy, and coverage model.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
