&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We are seeking a highly skilled and Technical Enablement Manager to focus on the enablement of our post sales teams; including Solutions Architects (SAs), AI Outcomes Managers (AIOMs) and Support teams. This role will be pivotal in developing and implementing technical training strategies that enhance the technical acumen and effectiveness of our technical teams, driving performance, efficiency, and productivity. If you are a strategic, detail-oriented technical professional with a passion for technical enablement, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
