&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Data-driven: utilize metrics and objective measurements to assess success and improvement opportunities for customers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
